!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Register Intern</title>


<style>

    *{
        margin:0;
        padding:0;
        box-sizing:border-box;
        font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
    }

    body{
        background:#f4f7fc;
    }

    .container{
        width:600px;
        margin:50px auto;
        background:white;
        padding:35px;
        border-radius:15px;
        box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h1{
        text-align:center;
        color:#1e3a8a;
        margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    p{
        text-align:center;
        color:#666;
        margin-bottom:25px;
    }

    .error{
        background:#ffe5e5;
        color:#d90429;
        padding:12px;
        border-radius:8px;
        margin-bottom:20px;
        text-align:center;
        font-weight:bold;
    }

    label{
        display:block;
        margin-bottom:8px;
        margin-top:15px;
        font-weight:600;
    }

    input{
        width:100%;
        padding:12px;
        border:1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius:8px;
    }

    button{
        width:100%;
        margin-top:25px;
        padding:14px;
        border:none;
        border-radius:8px;
        background:#1e3a8a;
        color:white;
        font-size:16px;
        cursor:pointer;
    }

    button:hover{
        background:#2563eb;
    }

</style>
```

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">


<h1>Register New Intern</h1>

<p>Enter intern details below</p>

{% if error %}
    <div class="error">
        {{ error }}
    </div>
{% endif %}

<form method="POST">

    <label>Full Name</label>
    <input
        type="text"
        name="name"
        value="{{ name }}"
        required
    >

    <label>Email Address</label>
    <input
        type="text"
        name="email"
        value="{{ email }}"
        required
    >

    <label>Domain</label>
    <input
        type="text"
        name="domain"
        value="{{ domain }}"
        required
    >

    <label>Duration</label>
    <input
        type="text"
        name="duration"
        value="{{ duration }}"
        required
    >

    <button type="submit">
        Register Intern
    </button>

</form>
```

</div>

</body>
</html>
